nodes.text: Tillin'natiri was a smuggler who once ran a con where they and their companions would dress as stormtroopers and "confiscate" cargo from other smugglers. However, they could only procure E-11 blaster rifles for the ruse rather than Stormtrooper Ones, causing at least one mark to figure out the con. Tillin'natiri detailed the scam on Gundark's Gear Datalog, where fellow smuggler Roark Garnet realized he had also been a victim of the con.
